to add user -useradd <username>
to set passwd for user - passwd <username>
to create group - groupadd <groupname>
to change group name - groupmod -n new_group_name old_group_name
to add user to group - usermod -aG <username> or gpasswd -a <username> <groupname>
to deleted a user from a grp - gpasswd -d <username> <groupname>
to delete a group - groupdel <groupname>
to check the groups the user is part of - id <usernmae>
